are you loading image library?

$config['source_image'] = $this-&gt;data['full_path'];
$config['new_image'] = $this-&gt;image_path;

'source_image' mean full path of your image folder with image name.
'new_image' mean full path of your image folder with image name in which your image have to store after resize.
